{"body": "+1 on *request* tests.  Acceptance testing has been the prevalent test type long before automated testing was known to more than 1% of developers, and it is still something that most enterprise projects can not be done without manual testing.  Taking a term with a long history and slapping it onto something that fits in the framework at hand is exactly the mistake that we are trying to fix by renaming 'unit tests' to 'model tests'.  Please don't repeat that mistake.\r\n\r\n(I know that I make exact and unsubstantiated claims above, but I hope that you agree with the reasoning anyway.)", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9252961", "created_at": "2012-10-09T08:31:01Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7878#issuecomment-9252961", "updated_at": "2012-10-09T08:31:01Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7878, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dvrensk", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/94952ae2519ff1b9b5d982863bcb37f3?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F050553d40196ef109fff37cbb40aaf28.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/received_events", "gravatar_id": "94952ae2519ff1b9b5d982863bcb37f3", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dvrensk", "type": "User", "id": 14046, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dvrensk/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f7febd3543c15100b190"}, "id": 9252961, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/